column5: Hey all... just issued by environment Canada, severe weather watch for most of Southern Ontario! Here we go again! http://www.weatheroffice.gc.ca/warnings/re..._e.html?onrm126 Take care if your heading out on the water or highway! HH  Edit... looks like ya beat me by a minute dsn!
Hmmm...last time this happened the Carp bite turned on big time later in the evenin....looks like I gotta go fishing tonite...LOL
What time should I meet you Cliff?
